                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 3691/454.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Chargé <persName type="from">Brown</persName> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Amapala</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1907-04-23">
                            <hi rend="italic">April 23, 1907</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Reports that peace terms have been agreed upon in principle and that the treaty
                    should be signed to-day. Adds that the ministers leave to-night.</p>
            </div>
